title: Macak pod sljemom (1962) Partizanski film
description:
Macak pod sljemom (1962) Partizanski film


Divna ratna prica o drvoseci koji je otisao u partizane.  Jugoslovenski ratni film o partizanima.



A tragicomic tale of lumberjack who joined the partisans during WW2. As a corporal, he successfully and courageously fulfilled the combat tasks with his partisan battalion. The commander sends him on a special assignment.


Language: Serbian
Director: Zorz Skrigin
Writer: Joza Horvat
Stars: Pavle Vuisic, Dragomir Bojanic-Gidra, Davor Antolic 



Reality Ascent by Dragan Glavasic
Wake up!
